{"title":"The Fairweather Bullmoose Bar Now Comes in a 750 mm Wide B923","link":"https://theradavist.com/fairweather-bullmoose-bar-now-comes-in-wide-b923/","date":1747059932000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>No need <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/add-40mm-of-overall-width-to-your-favorite-mtb-bar-with-the-control-tech-terminator-bar-extender-plugs/\" target=\"_blank\">for bar extenders now</a>! Japanese bike shop <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/blue-lug/\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Lug</a> just announced that the beloved <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/my-hunter-cycles-rigid-29r-is-sketchy-fun/\" target=\"_blank\">Fairweather bullmoose bars</a> now come in a wide option, B923. Blue Lug worked with Nitto to widen the width and extension of these Ritchey-inspired bars. The resulting bars became 40 mm wider than the B903, making the B923 bars 750 mm wide…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/54479313413_90f727e522_k.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/54479313413_90f727e522_k.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/54479313413_90f727e522_k.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/54479313413_90f727e522_k.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug_02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug_02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Fairweather_Bullmoose_Wide_Blue_Lug_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Other tweaks to the B923 include raising the bar ends to have a 10 mm upsweep, the extension of the integrated stem is 10 mm longer, and the whole bar is fillet brazed at the steerer for added durability.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>bar width : 750mm</li>\n<li>back sweep : 15°</li>\n<li>bar diameter : 22.2mm</li>\n<li>steerer size : 1-1/8″</li>\n<li>stack height : 40mm</li>\n<li>extension : 135mm(based off the NITTO UI-2 stem 100mm)</li>\n<li>material：chromoly steel</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The B923 comes in <a href=\"https://global.bluelug.com/fairweather-b923-bullmoose-bar-black.html\" target=\"_blank\">black</a> or <a href=\"https://global.bluelug.com/fairweather-b923-bullmoose-bar-dull.html\" target=\"_blank\">silver dull</a> and ships globally from <a href=\"https://global.bluelug.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Blue Lug’s international store</a> for around $25 to the CUSA…</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/fairweather-bullmoose-bar-now-comes-in-wide-b923/\">The Fairweather Bullmoose Bar Now Comes in a 750 mm Wide B923</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"a927558d664bd5ce73d712b0d0ebb59d85eaaa612953cb210849f93737a58094","category":"Cycling"}